n the guild (cue fanfare)..\n6) I set about recoding the add_actions in soul one by one...\n\nTHe one thing I wanted to ask was about spells.  At the moment these\nare in \"/players/redsexy/guild/spells\" and that dir doesn't\nload as all spells are referrential to declarations in the soul.\nIs that standard?\n\nActually if I could get someone to show me how to move an add_action\nto a bin command that'd be cool.  Any suggestions who?\n\nRight sleepybyes for me, for a little while,\n\nRed (hopefully able to conect to ICQ soon)\n\n\n**\nexos\n**\nTo: mangla\nSubj: Bard Guild\nCc: turbo\nDate: Mar 16\n\nI have installed Bard Guild into /players/turbo/guild.\nIt is working out of there right now...\n( I have /p/e/guild/soul.c and /p/e/guild/room.c inheriting his copies).\nWhen you get a chance can you update /guild/master?\n\nI think I worked all all the bugs tonight.\nIf any more arise, I will fix tomorrow.\nAs it is bards can log in fine.\n\n**\nexos\n**\nTo: mangla\nSubj: /room/plane5.c\nCc: turbo\nDate: Mar 16\n\nThis room needs to be changed to point to the bard room\nin Turbo's directory instead of mine now.\n\n**\nexos\n**\nTo: mangla\nSubj: Taliesin\nCc: turbo\nDate: Mar 16\n\nIts late, and I am not feeling that well.\nI also need the room changed that loads Taliesin.\nNeed him to load from Turbo's directory.\n\nI can't remember which file it is!\nI guess you can grep?\n\n**\ndarastor\n**\nTo: mangla\nSubj: barb guild\nDate: Mar 16\n\nLater today I'll be mailing you a list of where i think all the\nconnections to barb guild areas are\nin the main part of the mud, and asking you to point them\natthe code in my dir.\n\nD\n\n**\ndarastor\n**\nTo: mangla\nSubj: ryu armour\nDate: Mar 16\n\nI see ninja can now get an autoloading armour from ryu.\nWhile I don't know how powerful the armour is, I would hope\nthat you can check it out and make sure it's not obscenely powerful for an autoload armour\nsince by killing ryu they already get the best \nweapon on the mud (at 